{"tid":1678187,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「既事奉上帝，又事奉瑪門」 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-10-27T13:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T13:59:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"46f746f4041ed4c9a55f14b5be75a93917455b8b","tid":1678187,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T13:55:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191027/20794437/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191027%2F20794437%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4RQ2JDI1%2B2PXXyGzAukhOpM%3D&h=b066e976\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191027%2F20794437%2F&h=2f90f389\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191027/20794437/</a><br />\n<br />\n「既事奉上帝，又事奉瑪門」 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191027/large/1572080632_b7a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191027%2Flarge%2F1572080632_b7a2.jpg&h=ff37804c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳同佳洗黑錢案出獄後，面對殺人案的公義審判，是否變了一鑊泡？<br />\n<br />\n以「教徒」林鄭的政治盲狀況，不管想什麼說甚麼幹什麼（包括在日皇德仁登基大典無聊滑手機），都是錯。正因權位名利私慾，陳同佳送台審判本是單一事件，司法互助可特事特辦，彰顯公義不難，只是她為了搞天怒人怨的《逃犯條例》修訂，不肯好好處理，如今兩頭唔到岸，兩面不是人。想把陳同佳這燙手山芋扔給台方，人家小英谷底反彈，怎肯被「一國」矮化？怎甘不循司法程序為你「私了」釋懷？幫你毒招贖罪？<br />\n<br />\n陳同佳短短數月便信了教，甘願自首（投案），「被自首」嗎？有無安家費？有無誤導？是否政治棋子？若非一鼓作氣就逮，在花花世界拖延時日，「教徒」政棍鼠王芬屎橋：為免成為政治籌碼，可待台灣明年一月大選後才去自首──自由身的釋囚，享用公帑「保護」，如果到時不肯了，跑掉了，奈何？<br />\n<br />\n真詭異！最詭異的是「勸說者」中間人，管浩鳴紅底政協「牧師」的油滑張揚角色：策劃部署、拍攝需時、高調曝光、盛大公映、隨片登台&hellip;&hellip;續集劇本編寫中，拍戲咩？一看，原來是明年聖公會港島教區主教三名候選人之一，其「熱心」有助選情云云。明晒！ <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"d6fb560bdde9b62868475c228fc360b14e9ea524","tid":1678187,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T13:59:40.000Z","msg":"巴絲請將今日的警暴情況/記者中槍的tweets推上國際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4RQ2JDI1%2B2PXXyGzAukhOpM%3D&h=3931f2d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n入<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> /task1 </span></span>  retweet and like all links<br />\n入<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> /task2</span></span>    retweet and like all links"}]}